      "id": "metrics-content",
      "x": 530,
      "y": 800,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 170,
      "text": "Webinar goal:        50-100 per session\nWebinar close rate:  5-10%\nNew members/webinar: 2.5-10 people\n\nMONTHLY WEBINAR REVENUE:\n4 webinars x 5 avg closes x $997\n= ~$20K/mo from webinars alone\n\nDiscovery calls → Agency/Agents = additional",
